  -------- ---- ----- ---- --- Source df SS MS F Groups 2 Error 30 240 Total 32 340 -------- ---- ----- ---- ---

The test for the null hypothesis ANOVA can be performed at a significance level of 0.05

Answerlist
----------

* Be rejected

Solution
========

Answerlist

* Not be rejected: Incorrect
* Be rejected: Correct
